ygData.messageBody:
Ok,

So I've camped and I've camped and I have yet to be rewarded for my efforts
with even a single fang. I have however gained a few levels (both here in
sunny Mistmore and elsewhere) and I've noticed that the maid butler camp has
a relatively low amount of spawns, especially when trying to support 5 level
37 players.

Sooooooo...

Here's my question to all of you more experienced bards: What level can I
expect to have a reasonable shot at soloing the maid butler area? I'd be
quite content to just do the maid and butler room, and leave the hall and
kitchen alone.

Thanks in advance

Draelon Stormsong
the Tribunal
